"1/2 cup chicken or vegetable broth","1/3 cup hoisin sauce","1/4 cup soy sauce","1 tablespoon cornstarch","1/2  to 1 teaspoon chili-garlic paste or sriracha","12 ounces pork tenderloin, cut into strips","3  baby bok choy or 1 medium bok choy","5 teaspoons stir-fry oil or vegetable oil, divided","6  garlic cloves, sliced","1 tablespoon minced fresh ginger","2  shallots, halved and sliced","1  red bell pepper, thinly sliced","8 ounces cremini mushrooms, sliced","  Hot cooked soba noodles or rice noodles"